<item>
            <title>[LU-309] sanity test_27z does not work on loop device</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-309</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;symptom:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;got this error msg &quot;umount: /tmp/lustre-ost1: not mounted&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;root cause:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;for local device&lt;br/&gt;
   &quot;do_facet ost$devnum umount -d $dev&quot;  turns out to be &quot;umount /tmp/lustre-ost1&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
should be changed to&lt;br/&gt;
    local mntpt=$(facet_mntpt ost$devnum)&lt;br/&gt;
    do_facet ost$devnum umount -d $mntpt&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
